4. A fourth peculiar Name of Chriſt is the Name Jeſus. TheMat. 1. 22. Luke 1. 30. 
                  Angel you know gave him that Name, Matth. 1. and gave alſo the reaſon of it, becauſe he was to ſave his People from their ſins;


he therefore came into the world, that we might be ſaved from our Enemies, and from the hands of all that hated us. When old Simeon had him in his Arms, he called him The Lord's Salvation. Jeſus ſignifies a Saviour. Theſe are ſome of his perſonal Names, every one of which is to the Soul as a ſweet Oil, or Ointment poured forth.

